name: July 14th Enrollment for Team Pinching Inches
description:
Thank you for joining the 1st ever Team Pinching Inches Get Fit Challenge! Please bring your positive attitudes and determination with you on this journey to a healthier happier you!

Documents will be emailed to you once you enroll. Please be sure to include your email adress during enrollment.. this is the one that all of the information will be sent to. ENROLLMENT FEE IS NON-REFUNDABLE.

I look forward to starting & finising this fun and exciting journey with all of you!
